FBIS3-34944 "drnes032_k_94015" FBIS-NES-94-032 Document Type:Daily Report 16 Feb 1994 IRAQ Saddam's Son-in-Law Undergoes Treatment in Amman NC1202155494 (Clandestine) Voice of Iraqi People in Arabic 1400 GMT 12 Feb 94 NC1202155494 (Clandestine) Voice of Iraqi People Language: Arabic Article Type:BFN [Text] Well-informed sources in London and Amman yesterday disclosed that [Minister of Industry and Minerals] Husayn Kamil Hasan, the tyrant's son-in-law and the man in charge of military production, is undergoing treatment for a pernicious disease [euphemism for cancer] in an Amman hospital. [Words indistinct] Kamil was urgently flown by a military helicopter and admitted to al-Husayn Medical Center in Amman.
